{"article_id":"AxAkWerWPEoxBa25","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Republicans tried to build support Wednesday for their compromise immigration plan ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"they ' ve come up with something","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that can unite the GOP","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"and get President Trump ' s signature .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Preparing for the first major House immigration floor debate in eight years ,","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Speaker Paul D. Ryan was hashing out final details on the compromise ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"which he will put up for votes next week .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"\" This has a chance","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"of going into law , \"","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Mr. Ryan said","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"after a party caucus meeting Wednesday .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"According to a draft outline ,","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"the plan","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"the GOP is working on","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"would allow \" Dreamers , \" those","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"who illegally crossed into the U.S. as children ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"to get in line for citizenship .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"The plan would also authorize and fund Mr. Trump ' s border wall ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"raise the burden of proof on asylum claims ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"allow faster deportation of some illegal immigrants","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"including children ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"limit the chain of family migration","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"and eliminate the diversity visa lottery","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"that doles out 55,000 immigration passes each year .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"And the bill would explicitly prevent separation of children from their parents at the border ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"according to the draft .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Still to be decided is the size and details of the pathway to citizenship .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"One option would only cover Dreamers ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"while another option would cover children","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"whose parents came on temporary legal visas .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"The White House signaled its support for the plan ,","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"though many rank-and-file Republicans were waiting to see the final bill .","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"Rep. Mark Meadows , the head of the conservative Freedom Caucus , said","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"the president could sway members .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"\" Could he move 100 people","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"because he says","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"he likes it ?","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"The answer is ' No , ' \"","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Mr. Meadows said .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"\" Can he move a dozen or so ?","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"The answer is ' Yes. ' \"","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"GOP leaders dodged a bullet this week","depth":4},{"id":43,"text":"after a renegade group of moderate Republicans failed to muster enough support for a petition drive","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"that would have forced voted on a series of bills ,","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"including a Democrat-backed option with a more generous amnesty and far less enforcement .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"Instead , the GOP will allow two votes :","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"one on the compromise","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"still being worked out ,","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"and the other on an enforcement-heavy bill","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"authored by House Judiciary Chairman Bob Goodlatte .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"Mr. Goodlatte ' s bill would write President Obama ' s Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals program into law ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"granting Dreamers a firmer legal footing","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"but without the new pathway to citizenship","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"that many have demanded .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Instead , the attention is on the compromise ,","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"which","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"Mr. Ryan says","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"matches the four pillars of reform","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Mr. Trump laid out earlier this year .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"\" We ' ve been working hand-in-glove with the administration on this ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"to make sure","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"that we ' re bringing a bill","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"that represents the president ' s four pillars","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"so that we can come together ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"have the votes","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"that everybody ' s looking for , \"","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s \" four pillars \" blueprint called for a pathway to citizenship for up to 1.8 million illegal immigrants ,","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"combined with his border wall , elimination of the visa lottery and limits to the number of family members","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"a legal immigrant could sponsor .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"Rep. Scott Perry , Pennsylvania Republican and member of the Freedom Caucus , said","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"the \" devil is in the details \" of the compromise","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"- in particular when it comes to security .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"\" We all just need to take a breath","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"and see what we ' ve got","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"before we get too excited about it one way or the other , \"","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"Mr. Perry said .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":155,"left":119,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":89,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":82,"right":88,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":0,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"le